{"tid":901511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港奴悲劇！沒有固定住所 收工後網吧流連 外賣工人網吧內猝死！","createTime":"2018-11-14T05:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T04:47:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b0510fe7913a92ed48c8b78ec0f76adbf7215dfe","tid":901511,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"長沙灣男子網吧內猝死。今早(14日)10時18分，元州街152號一間廿四小時營業的網吧，職員發現一名年約50歲男顧客昏迷，拍他未有反應，遂報警求助。救援人員到場，證實男子已經死去，警員在場調查其死因，初步相信未有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男子為一名送外賣工人，惟因沒有固定住所，有人在每晚11時收工後，便到網吧流連。死者本身患有血管疾病，今早職員見他坐於櫈上昏睡，初時以為他「瞓過龍」，但稍後擬拍醒他時，發現他身體僵硬，大驚報警。警方調查後，列作發現屍體處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181114/bkn-20181114111432302-1114_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181114%2Fbkn-20181114111432302-1114_00822_001.html&d=NFFS3mC8m57zLGIwnaKavcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7cf07814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181114/bkn-20181114111432302-1114_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"086233adb66c4946b62980df4573627e815ba586","tid":901511,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"返工=??"},{"pid":"c29682f944cbd45850bbb72a1a152babb8e6cd56","tid":901511,"uid":64009,"like":4,"dislike":72,"score":-68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"廢柴"},{"pid":"4bb922e6afc5385a47b9843c479548f3d47e6263","tid":901511,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔訓公園？"},{"pid":"19c86dc85c3176a3ae5af8ce16411a604817b52c","tid":901511,"uid":19454,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"4bb922e6afc5385a47b9843c479548f3d47e6263","tid":901511,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔訓公園？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"冇冷氣"},{"pid":"a5552fadba24dd5df4c525668a3bd3a8caa06cf2","tid":